According to a family member, France Sibanyoni, the truck was overtaking at the T-junction near Blinkwater Mills when it collided head-on with the Corolla.All three occupants of the vehicle were declared dead on the scene and the car they were travelling in was a total wreckage.The deceased are all residents of the farm Nooitgedacht and were on their way home when the accident occurred.One has been identified as Thapelo Posman Makua, and the names of the other two men who died could not be established at the time of going to print.